OL,8,Fcruelty and murder
OL,10,FA mother who beat, caned and burned
OL,11,Fher three-year-old son has been
OL,12,Fsentenced to life in prison for his
OL,13,Fmurder.
OL,15,FChristina Robinson had exposed her son
OL,16,FDwelaniyah to cruelty and excruciating
OL,17,Fpain over several weeks before she
OL,18,Fshook him to death at the family home
OL,19,Fin Bracken Court, Ushaw Moor, Durham,
OL,20,Fin November 2022.
