OL,4,Cmurdering son in 'campaign of violence'
OL,6,FA trial at Newcastle Crown Court heard
OL,7,Fshe had deliberately immersed him in
OL,8,Fscalding water, causing severe burns
OL,9,Fthat left him in agony.
OL,11,FThe 30-year-old was also found guilty
OL,12,Fof four child cruelty offences, which
OL,13,Fhappened in the weeks leading up to
OL,14,Fhis death.
OL,16,FAt sentencing, the judge handed
OL,17,FRobinson a life sentence, whereby she
OL,18,Fmust serve a minimum of 25 years in
OL,19,Fprison.
