OL,10,FMr Justice Garnham addressed Robinson,
OL,11,Fstating: "What must have gone through
OL,12,Fthe mind of this little boy, being
OL,13,Fbeaten with a cane by his mother,
OL,14,Fdespite these terrible burns, does not
OL,15,Fbear thinking about."
OL,17,FDuring the hearing, Robinson once
OL,18,Fagain "declined representation" but
OL,19,Ftold the court:
