OL,6,FDuring the at Newcastle Crown Court,
OL,7,Fthe prosecution set out how Robinson
OL,8,Fdeliberately scalded the little boy as
OL,9,Fa punishment, how she hit him with
OL,10,Fspoons, slapped him and beat him with
OL,11,Fa bamboo cane, how she did not seek
OL,12,Fmedical attention for his burns.
OL,14,FThe court also heard how she neglected
OL,15,Fhim by repeatedly leaving her children
OL,16,Fat home alone while she conducted an
OL,17,Faffair while her husband was away
OL,18,Fserving with the RAF.
