OL,6,FRobinson, who represented herself ,
OL,7,Ftold the jury in her closing speech on
OL,8,FTuesday 19 March: "Please do not find
OL,9,Fme guilty for something I have not
OL,10,Fdone."
OL,12,FBut a jury found her guilty of all
OL,13,Fcharges, and today (24 May) she was
OL,14,Ftold she will serve a minimum of a
OL,15,Fquarter of a century behind bars.
