OL,6,FThe defendant, originally from
OL,7,FTamworth, Staffordshire, took more
OL,8,Fthan 20 minutes before dialling 999 on
OL,9,Fthe day of the fatal incident, first
OL,10,Fspeaking to her husband on the phone
OL,11,Fdespite him serving with the RAF 240
OL,12,Fmiles away, and then using Google to
OL,13,Flook at how to resuscitate a child.
OL,15,FWhen the emergency services arrived,
OL,16,FRobinson appeared calm as she
OL,17,Fexplained her version of events to a
OL,18,Fpolice officer while medics worked
OL,19,Fdesperately on Dwelaniyah.
