OL,6,FIn a statement, Detective Chief
OL,7,FInspector Simon Turner, Senior
OL,8,FInvestigating Officer for Operation
OL,9,FAruana at Durham Constabulary, said:
OL,10,F"Dwelaniyah was a defenceless little
OL,11,Fboy who had his life ahead of him, but
OL,12,Fthis was cruelly taken away his own
OL,13,Fmother ` someone he should have been
OL,14,Fable to trust, someone who should have
OL,15,Fcared about him.
OL,17,F"We may never know why or what caused
OL,18,FChristina Robinson to do what she did.
