OL,6,F"Her actions are unforgivable and
OL,7,Fsadly nothing will bring Dwelaniyah
OL,8,Fback but at least she is now facing
OL,9,Fthe consequences of what she has done.
OL,11,F"This has been a truly heartbreaking
OL,12,Fand emotional case for everyone
OL,13,Finvolved, including my investigation
OL,14,Fteam, who have worked tirelessly to
OL,15,Fbring Robinson to justice.
OL,17,F"My thoughts remain with those who
OL,18,Floved and cared about Dwelaniyah."
